tjceu.quest.db.57.title=Super Tank I
tjceu.quest.db.57.desc=Super tanks and super chests can be used to hold bulk quantities of fluids and items from LV onwards. These hold 32000 buckets and 2048000 items, respectively, so it should be plenty of storage for any short - medium term needs. %n%nThese also retain their contents when broken.
tjceu.quest.db.58.title=Basic Chemical Reactor
tjceu.quest.db.58.desc=You'll need thousands of chemical reactors if you're playing the pack correctly. For now, one is enough to get started. Maybe wait until you have better circuits before mass producing machines?
