tjceu.quest.db.74.title=Refined Processor
tjceu.quest.db.74.desc=This is the cheapest LV circuit you will get for a while, at least until you unlock the SoC recipe at a higher voltage tier. It may not seem like much, but remember you used to have to make primitve processors 1 at a time.%n%nThe advent of SMD technology and plastic boards allows for compact and efficent processors.
