tjceu.quest.db.97.title=Digital Interface Cover
tjceu.quest.db.97.desc=Digital covers can be useful for many purposes such as; viewing/interacting with the item/fluids in a block, viewing energy details, redstone control, and proxy mode for use with the central monitor. Use a screwdriver to enter the GUI.
