tjceu.quest.db.125.title=Man it can be fun to cheat
tjceu.quest.db.125.desc=If you would like to use astral purely as a Tech mod with great QOL, use this quest to completely skip over all of astrals research progression and learn all constellations.
tjceu.quest.db.126.title=Reactor Steel
