tjceu.quest.db.127.title=Reactor Types
tjceu.quest.db.127.desc=You will need to make either a nuclear reactor or a breeder reactor. The breeder is more complicated to automate, requires IV components, and needs some U-235 already separated (you can get this from ore processing). However, it rewards with better yields and enables you to skip rungs on the nuclear ladder, which you'll learn about soon.
tjceu.quest.db.128.title=Heat Exchanger
tjceu.quest.db.128.desc=The heat exchanger will use water in one input hatch and lava in another, and produce both hot steam and pahoehoe lava, which can be electrolyzed for carbon,%n sulfur, and obsidian. The hot steam can be either voided, or used in a coolant turbine for a considerable amount of power.
tjceu.quest.db.129.title=Tungstate Dust
tjceu.quest.db.129.desc=Tungsten is mined from the end
