tjceu.quest.db.657.title=Energy Hatches
tjceu.quest.db.657.desc=Gregtech energy hatches can take in two amps of power of their respective tier. To make one amp of the next tier for a multiblock you can use two energy hatches. This would equal 4 amps on one tier or 1 amp of the next.
