tjceu.quest.db.814.title=Maintenance Hatch
tjceu.quest.db.814.desc=Maintenance can be dealt with in 2 ways. One is to have the tools that correspond to the errors in the multiblocks controller in your inventory and press the square in the hatch.%n%nThe other is to have duct tape in your inventory and press the square in the hatch, duct tape will remove all issues.%n%nAgain, the square in the hatch is a button, not a slot. You don't need to drag anything to it, just click it when you have the appropriate item(s) in your inventory. %n%nRemember not to try and share these between multiblocks -- everything else is fine.
