tjceu.quest.db.1319.title=Electric Blast Furnace
tjceu.quest.db.1319.desc=This is needed to process stronger metals. Recipes in the EBF have a heat requirement (dictated by the coils used in the structure) as well as an energy requirements. To make your first aluminum, you will need to have 2 LV energy input hatches which can each accept up to 2 amps of LV, for a total of 128 EU/t.
