tjceu.quest.db.1324.title=ULV Machine Hull
tjceu.quest.db.1324.desc=Machine hulls are needed to craft all tiers of machines, hatches, and busses. There are no ULV machines (if you just thought 'technically there is an ore washer' then I don't like you), but there are ULV busses and hatches. This is what your first machine hulls will be for.
tjceu.quest.db.1325.title=Rutherfordium Boule
tjceu.quest.db.1325.desc=You can now make rutherfordium boules. They are relatively expensive for you at the moment, but may be worth it for the increased chip yeild and new %nrecipe unlocks. Plus, you'll need them later for HASoCs.
